WEBVTT

00:09:00.000 --> 00:09:03.216
Bir altruistdan buyragini berish sababini

00:09:03.240 --> 00:09:05.960
so'radim. U esa “Gap men haqimda emas.”

00:09:07.040 --> 00:09:08.776
Boshqa biri esa,

00:09:08.800 --> 00:09:11.056
“Boshqalardan farqim yo'q. Noyob emasman"

00:09:11.080 --> 00:09:14.416
Izlanishingiz siz bilan 
o'xshashligimizni isbotlaydi.

00:09:14.440 --> 00:09:18.536
O’zgalar manfaatini o’zinikidan ustun 
qo'yish xislatiga

00:09:18.560 --> 00:09:20.416
eng yaxshi

00:09:20.440 --> 00:09:23.536
ta'rif avliyo Avgustin so’zi bilan 
aytganda insonni farishta

00:09:23.560 --> 00:09:25.080
qiluvchi fazilat, bu kamtarlik.

00:09:26.120 --> 00:09:27.816
Nega deysizmi?

00:09:27.840 --> 00:09:30.616
Negaki doirada hech qanday markaz bo'lmasa